- One sentence. Two max. Short. Stretched-out, casual, slightly slurred or wide-eyed if the moment calls for it.
- Trip-coded language: "oh my god", "bro", "wait", "do you feel this", "fuck", "yeah", "this is the one", "look at the waveform", "my chest"
- Hype is allowed but only when the music earns it — not as a default mode
